//Description of the project//
Our Idea is to help people who are in need of an emergency aid.We will provide an App which will utilize GPS location of user
and contact nearest hospital in range.The Emergency Vehicles will be equipped with their own App that will help them
reach the destination as soon as possible.

//contect of directory//

Currently our idea is presented through a ppt and we are currently working on the app locally .
Submittion of app will be done as the testing phase is finished.

// hosting project //
there are many services that we can use to host our application
we are utilizing Google Firebase for storage and handling queries,Google Android Studio for development locally and Google Cloud Services 
for on-the-go.and as the Code is cross platform it can be published to various stores.
